Rich Cimini
@RichCimini
·
31s
Daniel Jeremiah (
@MoveTheSticks
), just now on a media conference call, says “all signs” that he’s aware of point to the #Jets waiting until 2027 to draft their QB of the future. In other words, he’d be surprised if they take QB Ty Simpson at 16.
